      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 17.238181,
      "replayEndSec": 21.33289,
      "narrationText": "One handy option: open the repo directly in VS Code with this command. We won't launch the editor here, but it starts a remote session into the repo over SSH so you can edit its files.",
